<main>
    <header>
        <h1>
            <div style="font-weight: 300; color: var(--medium);">{{ collections.polaroids | length }}</div> Polaroids of Folk That Make Music
            <span>© James Perou</span>
        </h1>

        <details>
            <summary>
                <b>About the project</b>
            </summary>
            <p style="padding-top: 0.5em;">"Polaroids Of Folk That Make Music" is a long-term photography project born from a passion for live music and a deep-seated addiction to Polaroid film. Starting in 2007, the project features over 3000 unique Polaroid portraits of musicians, captured backstage and at venues, with a strict "one Polaroid per person" rule. The series embraces the unique, unrepeatable nature of instant film, capturing authentic reactions without direction.</p>
        </details>

    </header>

    <section style="position: relative;">

        <nav>
            <small>To search for an artist, use <kbd>^Ctrl</kbd> / <kbd>⌘Cmd</kbd> + <kbd>F</kbd>
            </small>

            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">Email</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <ul class="list">
            {% set sorted = collections.polaroids | sort(attribute = 'data.pagination_pageNumber') | reverse %}
            {% for polaroid in sorted %}
                <li>
                    <figure>
                        <div class="img_wrap">
                            <img alt="" width="300" height="365" loading="lazy" src="{{ polaroid.data.img_src }}"/>
                            {% if polaroid.data.onmouseover_src %}
                                <img class="img_hover" alt=""  width="300" height="365" loading="lazy" src="{{ polaroid.data.onmouseover_src }}"/>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                        <figcaption>
                            <h2>
                                {{ polaroid.data.musician_name | safe }}
                                <span>{{ polaroid.data.band_name | safe }}</span>
                            </h2>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>

    </section>
</main>

